Our FLEXI fares not only give flexibility but also convenience, simplicity and save you time. These are all the great services you can enjoy when you buy a FLEXI ticket: 
	Speedy Boarding 
	Allocated seating 
	Fast Track security 
	Change to an earlier flight for free 
	One piece of cabin luggage (unlimited weight) 
	A second piece of cabin luggage: small under the seat bag (handbag/ laptop) 
	One piece of hold luggage (23kg max.) 
	No extra booking fees 
	Free route changes (unless the new fare is higher, then the applicable difference applies) 
	Unlimited free date changes in a 4 week period - from 1 week before to 3 weeks after the original travel date
	Food & drink voucher to be used on board your Flight for up to £7.50

The carbon emissions from the fuel used for all of our flights will be offset.

www.easyjet.com
